5px;">Volcano bonds</h2>
</td>
</tr>
</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Maybe the one trade I have ever sugges=
ted in this column (still not financial advice!) <a href=3D"https://link.ma=
il.bloombergbusiness.com/click/27201820.262606/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJn=
